[The number of cases of hantavirus pulmonary syndrome (HPS) reported from
North and South America has increased in recent weeks. Therefore, for the
time being, reports of HPS from North and South America will be combined
and posted in the form of updates at intervals determined by the frequency
of such reports. - Mod.CP]

In this update:

[1] Uruguay - Rocha
[2] Brazil (Federal District, Goias)

